Queries :

1. Get the total number of movies that are released in year 1991

2. Get the least rank for a movies

3. Get the maximum rank for movies that are released in year 2000

4. Get the average ranking for movies that are released in year 2000

5. Find the total number of unique years in the imdb database given to you.

6. Find the time period that this database covers. (start year, end year)

Solutions :

Q1="SELECT COUNT(name) FROM Movie WHERE year==1991;"

Q2="SELECT MIN(rank) FROM Movie;"

Q3="SELECT MAX(rank) FROM Movie WHERE year==2000;"

Q4="SELECT AVG(rank) FROM Movie WHERE year==2000;"

Q5="SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT year) FROM Movie;"

Q6="SELECT MIN(year),MAX(year) FROM Movie;"
